---
description: Search and compose before adding helpers; extract on the third copy
alwaysApply: true
---

# Reuse first

- Search for helpers/types/hooks before writing new ones.
- **Third duplicate → extract** shared logic.
- Put shared code in `shared/`, `lib/`, `utils/`, or an existing module—not buried in unrelated features.
- Small named exports; avoid giant “helpers” barrels.
- Update all call sites after extracting.
